sequenceDiagram
    participant Investor as Tech-Savvy Investor
    participant WebApp as Web Application
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant AuthService as Authentication Service
    participant KYC as KYC/AML System
    Investor->>WebApp: Access registration form
    WebApp->>API: Submit registration data
    API->>AuthService: Request authentication
    AuthService->>KYC: Verify identity
    KYC-->>AuthService: Verification result
    AuthService-->>API: Authentication token